reviewText: I cannot review this dvd because they sent me the wrong one twice. This is not Charles Starrett or Frontier Fury. It is the Lone Rider in Frontier Fury with Fuzzy Al St. John. Wrong actors and wrong title. I reported this mistake and I hope they resolve it so I can buy it. Your old western pal, Kevin Boyd
